          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Placing supplemental or reference information in the margin of your article can create an informative and engaging experience.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "On this page, you’ll learn how to create a sidebar that contains some HTML formatting.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
